author: cms-l1t-offline
body:
Removal of currently inactive parts of the seeding module, on top of  https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/13703 which was merged in CMSSW_8_1_X earlier today.
Integration into CMSSW_8_0_X is still ongoing in  https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/13702, so no need for a new PR there.
This will keep integration in CMSSW_8_1_X and CMSSW_8_0_X in sync.
title: Rekovic hlt 802 seed unpacked gt (pruning on top of PR 13703)
